0
00:00:07,719 --> 00:00:10,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胡萝卜硬得像铁块</font>

1
00:00:10,379 --> 00:00:13,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你犯下的最大错误 就是让我来做饭</font>

2
00:00:13,819 --> 00:00:15,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你为什么还能这么得意洋洋的？</font>

3
00:00:16,089 --> 00:00:19,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实是因为找不到平时那把菜刀…</font>

4
00:00:19,469 --> 00:00:21,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对 现在不是说这个的时候</font>

5
00:00:21,819 --> 00:00:25,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刻耳柏洛斯已经死了 这是确定无疑的</font>

6
00:00:26,249 --> 00:00:28,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然如此 那个冒牌的风靡小姐是？</font>

7
00:00:29,089 --> 00:00:33,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果那个假女警的真身是赫尔呢？</font>

8
00:00:33,649 --> 00:00:36,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">赫尔？但她也没有变身能力啊</font>

9
00:00:37,379 --> 00:00:41,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「人造人」是以某种东西为核心诞生的</font>

10
00:00:41,389 --> 00:00:45,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只要继承了那个核心 就能继承其特殊能力</font>

11
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:47,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是指…</font>

12
00:00:48,109 --> 00:00:50,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那块黑色的石头？</font>

13
00:00:50,959 --> 00:00:56,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就是说 赫尔现在继承了能力和使命 在掠夺人的心脏？</font>

14
00:00:56,889 --> 00:00:57,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就说不好了</font>

15
00:00:58,949 --> 00:01:02,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也可能纯粹是为了自己</font>

16
00:01:02,929 --> 00:01:06,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真能像换装洋娃娃那样换来换去？</font>

17
00:01:07,049 --> 00:01:10,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">能 因为敌人是「人造人」</font>

18
00:01:10,859 --> 00:01:13,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但即使如此 我们要做的事情也没有改变</font>

19
00:01:14,029 --> 00:01:17,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们要结束这宗连环杀人案</font>

20
00:01:18,089 --> 00:01:20,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感觉从明天开始就要忙起来了</font>

21
00:01:21,229 --> 00:01:24,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 但这样的话…</font>

22
00:01:24,899 --> 00:01:27,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要是顾虑我的话 那就大可不必</font>

23
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:30,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">艾丽西亚！你什么时候来的！</font>

24
00:01:32,179 --> 00:01:35,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这音效让人想象不出是在吃咖喱啊</font>

25
00:01:36,999 --> 00:01:40,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">总之 你们现在应该优先考虑案子的事情</font>

26
00:01:41,559 --> 00:01:45,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你应该不是为了说这种懂事的话 才特地跑到这里来的吧</font>

27
00:01:47,269 --> 00:01:50,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个案子 我也想给你们帮忙！</font>

28
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:53,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就知道你会这么说 但绝对不行</font>

29
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么？</font>

30
00:01:55,729 --> 00:01:59,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为很危险 已经出现4个死者了</font>

31
00:01:59,559 --> 00:02:03,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我在那两周里也和君冢一起解决过案子的！</font>

32
00:02:03,609 --> 00:02:06,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也就只是帮人找猫 把钱包送到派出所吧？</font>

33
00:02:06,989 --> 00:02:09,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">案…案子不分大小啦！</font>

34
00:02:09,849 --> 00:02:11,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是歪理</font>

35
00:02:11,189 --> 00:02:13,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">歪理也是道理！</font>

36
00:02:15,169 --> 00:02:16,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">冷静一下</font>

37
00:02:18,259 --> 00:02:20,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">人家也是侦探嘛</font>

38
00:02:21,579 --> 00:02:26,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">艾丽西亚 你只是个代理侦探 已经没有你出场的份了</font>

39
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:33,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 谢丝塔 你这话说得就过分了</font>

40
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:36,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么？你站在她那一边？</font>

41
00:02:36,989 --> 00:02:38,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我也没这么说啊</font>

42
00:02:38,959 --> 00:02:41,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 你果然偏爱小女孩</font>

43
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:45,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">咦 真的找不到菜刀啊</font>

44
00:02:45,239 --> 00:02:48,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要在这种时候去找那种危险的东西</font>

45
00:02:49,799 --> 00:02:50,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好吧</font>

46
00:02:51,699 --> 00:02:54,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我会用我的方式来行动</font>

47
00:02:55,219 --> 00:02:58,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个案子 就由我来解决</font>

48
00:02:58,819 --> 00:03:02,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这样就能证明我也是侦探了！</font>

49
00:03:03,259 --> 00:03:07,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是这样了 明天开始就拜托你啦 君冢</font>

50
00:03:09,779 --> 00:03:12,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 懂了 明白</font>

51
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:17,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">太好啦！所以 今后君冢也是我的助手啦！</font>

52
00:03:18,509 --> 00:03:20,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是 助手是…</font>

53
00:03:21,259 --> 00:03:24,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我的…我的…</font>

54
00:03:32,749 --> 00:03:39,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是第5个受害人被夺走心脏的警铃</font>

55
00:03:41,989 --> 00:03:45,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第8集 然后再次踏上旅程)</font>

56
00:03:45,019 --> 00:03:45,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 案子刚发生就来打扰
(第8集 然后再次踏上旅程)</font>

57
00:03:45,989 --> 00:03:48,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 案子刚发生就来打扰</font>

58
00:03:48,689 --> 00:03:55,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事 这是你们的工作吧 希望我能帮得上忙</font>

59
00:03:55,689 --> 00:03:57,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我去给你们倒茶</font>

60
00:04:00,029 --> 00:04:01,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你没事吧</font>

61
00:04:01,939 --> 00:04:06,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 因为事出突然 我至今还不相信…</font>

62
00:04:07,219 --> 00:04:11,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那孩子已经走了…</font>

63
00:04:15,339 --> 00:04:24,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">丈夫早早去世 我和女儿相依为命 让她一直吃苦</font>

64
00:04:25,029 --> 00:04:26,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但那孩子却总是说</font>

65
00:04:26,489 --> 00:04:31,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「我将来要赚很多很多钱 让妈妈过上好日子」</font>

66
00:04:32,379 --> 00:04:37,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">后来她真的很争气 甚至还给我建了这么间大房子</font>

67
00:04:37,769 --> 00:04:42,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">案件发生的那天 您的女儿有什么不正常的地方吗？</font>

68
00:04:44,499 --> 00:04:46,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 谢丝塔</font>

69
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:52,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那天她就是很正常地出了门</font>

70
00:04:52,689 --> 00:04:55,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么 有在遗体上发现什么不正常的吗？</font>

71
00:04:58,759 --> 00:04:59,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

72
00:05:01,849 --> 00:05:08,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那孩子是我引以为豪的女儿 好到我甚至都配不上她</font>

73
00:05:09,609 --> 00:05:13,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然而 我什么都没能给她</font>

74
00:05:14,819 --> 00:05:19,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一直在接受她的给予 却什么都没法回报…</font>

75
00:05:25,579 --> 00:05:27,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">才不是这样的呢！</font>

76
00:05:28,629 --> 00:05:34,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一味的接受？一味的给予？哪可能有这种单方面的关系！</font>

77
00:05:34,769 --> 00:05:39,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果你一直在接受你女儿的给予</font>

78
00:05:39,449 --> 00:05:44,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那肯定是因为你也给过你女儿很多东西啊！</font>

79
00:05:45,099 --> 00:05:46,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没错吧！</font>

80
00:05:53,879 --> 00:05:55,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢谢你</font>

81
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:59,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">简直好像是我女儿在对我说话一样</font>

82
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刚才…</font>

83
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么阻止我？</font>

84
00:06:16,269 --> 00:06:19,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这一连串案件 都是随机杀人</font>

85
00:06:20,569 --> 00:06:25,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以你问受害人是否有和平时不同的行为 根本毫无意义</font>

86
00:06:26,489 --> 00:06:31,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">之前的案件是这样而已 并不代表这次也一样</font>

87
00:06:31,739 --> 00:06:36,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哪怕是为了排除例外 我也有必要问那样的问题</font>

88
00:06:39,589 --> 00:06:45,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只要能击败赫尔 我会不择手段 一定要将她逼入绝境</font>

89
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:46,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是</font>

90
00:06:47,039 --> 00:06:48,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你并非如此啊</font>

91
00:06:50,329 --> 00:06:52,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔 我…</font>

92
00:06:53,659 --> 00:06:57,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你本来是我唯一信任的人了</font>

93
00:06:58,489 --> 00:06:59,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔…</font>

94
00:07:01,359 --> 00:07:04,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今天我先回去了 再见</font>

95
00:07:11,479 --> 00:07:14,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">别躲了 出来吧 艾丽西亚</font>

96
00:07:16,229 --> 00:07:18,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">呃…露馅了？</font>

97
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:24,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么说呢 那也是常有的事了</font>

98
00:07:24,799 --> 00:07:29,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟一起旅行了3年 吵架一两次也很正常</font>

99
00:07:29,829 --> 00:07:34,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反而是不吵才奇怪呢 这是常有的事了</font>

100
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:39,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 如此较真的对立可能还是第一次</font>

101
00:07:39,119 --> 00:07:44,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 怎么说呢 那个 所以…</font>

102
00:07:44,629 --> 00:07:46,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哇 你这不是很在意吗</font>

103
00:07:47,979 --> 00:07:49,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">别谈这个话题了</font>

104
00:07:50,999 --> 00:07:52,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说起来…</font>

105
00:08:00,649 --> 00:08:01,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">咦 这个…</font>

106
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是那时候的…</font>

107
00:08:06,419 --> 00:08:08,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 不过倒也算不上什么礼物吧</font>

108
00:08:11,799 --> 00:08:12,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好高兴</font>

109
00:08:13,809 --> 00:08:15,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这还是第一次…</font>

110
00:08:15,919 --> 00:08:18,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有人送我礼物呢</font>

111
00:08:19,459 --> 00:08:21,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">艾丽西亚 你…</font>

112
00:08:23,389 --> 00:08:24,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是啦 只是隐约有这种感觉</font>

113
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:31,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">失忆之前的我 肯定是个坏孩子吧</font>

114
00:08:39,119 --> 00:08:42,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说得好像你现在就不是个坏孩子一样</font>

115
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:45,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊？我可是超好的孩子啊！</font>

116
00:08:45,199 --> 00:08:48,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既开朗又可爱还坦率 人见人爱！</font>

117
00:08:48,779 --> 00:08:49,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好笑</font>

118
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好笑个头啊</font>

119
00:08:51,049 --> 00:08:53,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可恶</font>

120
00:08:54,909 --> 00:08:55,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂</font>

121
00:08:57,699 --> 00:08:59,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">帮我戴上戒指</font>

122
00:09:00,939 --> 00:09:01,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我来？</font>

123
00:09:02,439 --> 00:09:03,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你来</font>

124
00:09:04,079 --> 00:09:05,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给你戴？</font>

125
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我戴</font>

126
00:09:18,069 --> 00:09:20,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">戴错手指的话 我会生气的哦</font>

127
00:09:20,949 --> 00:09:22,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么伸出左手啊</font>

128
00:09:23,479 --> 00:09:25,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是装装样子哦</font>

129
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:37,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">双方发誓</font>

130
00:09:37,729 --> 00:09:40,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么你还兼职牧师了</font>

131
00:09:41,669 --> 00:09:43,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真是的</font>

132
00:09:45,749 --> 00:09:47,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 怎么说呢</font>

133
00:09:47,589 --> 00:09:50,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今后就勉勉强强地永远在一起？</font>

134
00:09:50,269 --> 00:09:53,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请多指教 就这样吧</font>

135
00:09:55,319 --> 00:09:57,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">总感觉一点都不严肃</font>

136
00:09:57,719 --> 00:09:59,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">烦死了 别要求那么多</font>

137
00:10:09,389 --> 00:10:10,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刚才我说得过分了</font>

138
00:10:12,299 --> 00:10:13,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔</font>

139
00:10:15,109 --> 00:10:21,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 我并不觉得自己的想法是错的 也不会轻易地扭转</font>

140
00:10:21,969 --> 00:10:27,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但也觉得单方面把自己的想法强加在别人身上是不好的</font>

141
00:10:27,219 --> 00:10:30,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但即使如此 你也有需要反省的地方…</font>

142
00:10:30,569 --> 00:10:35,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是 我并没有想过要旧事重提 总之…</font>

143
00:10:45,969 --> 00:10:47,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">祝两位幸福</font>

144
00:10:47,989 --> 00:10:49,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

145
00:10:54,889 --> 00:10:56,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂</font>

146
00:10:57,609 --> 00:11:00,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔 听到了吗？</font>

147
00:11:00,769 --> 00:11:01,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没听到</font>

148
00:11:02,969 --> 00:11:04,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是小孩子吗</font>

149
00:11:06,259 --> 00:11:11,139
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我说 谢丝塔 现在还没查出艾丽西亚的背景吗？</font>

150
00:11:11,869 --> 00:11:14,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不知道 我完全没查到</font>

151
00:11:19,609 --> 00:11:22,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">抱歉 我出趟门</font>

152
00:11:25,669 --> 00:11:27,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">未婚妻有危险了</font>

153
00:11:40,509 --> 00:11:41,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">艾丽西亚！</font>

154
00:11:44,589 --> 00:11:45,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你没事吧！</font>

155
00:11:47,879 --> 00:11:49,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">君冢…</font>

156
00:11:50,329 --> 00:11:51,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你坚持住…</font>

157
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:53,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">左胸被切开了</font>

158
00:11:54,489 --> 00:11:58,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然失去了意识 但应该没有生命危险</font>

159
00:12:00,349 --> 00:12:02,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个人是警察</font>

160
00:12:04,369 --> 00:12:05,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 助手</font>

161
00:12:07,019 --> 00:12:08,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">先叫救护车吧</font>

